suncertify.common

Interface AppConfigParam


  • public interface AppConfigParam
    This AppConfigParam interface defines the values used as keys in requesting application configuration parameters from the AppConfigManager.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Augustine Ogundimu
    See Also:
    AppConfigManager
